column10: At the SW corner of Lauren Elizabeth Lane and Gallows Road, a driver turned right with the crosswalk sign on.
Female driver didn't yield with pedestrian light on, and turned right into crosswalk at 7:27 AM

On Saturday at 6:34 PM, I was crossing Gallows Road from Prescott Dr to Lauren Elizabeth Lane with the active pedestrian signal. A car on Lauren Elizabeth Lane turned right onto Gallows Road into the crosswalk when I hadn't finished crossing.
